Comment: 0,0:00:00.96,0:00:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,845年
Comment: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因突然出現的超大型巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,和盔甲巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一切的日常與牆壁一同被摧毀
Comment: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類放棄了瑪利亞之牆
Comment: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,失去了兩成的人口以及三分之一的領土
Comment: 0,0:00:23.11,0:00:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類活動範圍退至羅塞之牆
Comment: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,850年
Comment: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因再次現身的超大型巨人 城牆被破壞
Comment: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類又再次地允許了巨人的進攻
Comment: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,士兵們接二連三地在巨人的面前倒下
Comment: 0,0:00:46.09,0:00:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後...
Comment: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點!
Comment: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,曾一度成為了巨人飼料的艾連．葉卡
Comment: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又再次地 從謎之巨人的身體中現身
Comment: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,集合!!
Comment: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,南側領土最高負責人
Comment: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,達特．皮克希斯
Comment: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看上在戰鬥中巨人化的艾連．葉卡的力量而下達某個決定
Comment: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,變成巨人後的他
Comment: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將會抬起前門附近的那顆大岩石
Comment: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,搬到被破壞的門旁
Comment: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將洞口封住
Comment: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,當這次作戰成功之時
Comment: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類將會是首次成功從巨人手中把領土給搶回來
Comment: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這一步
Comment: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將會是我們人類
Comment: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,偉大的進擊!!
Comment: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是這個作戰才剛開始
Comment: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就隨即面臨失敗
Comment: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Comment: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,勉強讓大部分的巨人聚集到城市的角落了
Comment: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然盡力避免了戰鬥
Comment: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但還是失去了大約兩成的士兵
Comment: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是失去了
Comment: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,士兵不是自己去送死
Comment: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是因為我的命令而死的
Comment: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在是關係到人類存亡的關鍵
Comment: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果是為了讓人類存活下去的話
Comment: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,即使被稱為殺戮者 我也無所謂
Comment: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿卡曼!!
Comment: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂! 阿卡曼別去!
Comment: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快離開他!
Comment: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連 你不認識我了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你的...
Comment: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,家人!
Comment: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你必須用那顆岩石把洞口封住!
Comment: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,作戰失敗了
Comment: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我就知道
Comment: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,根本就沒有秘密武器這回事
Comment: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連 你是人類!
Comment: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是...
Comment: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,閃開 阿卡曼!!
Comment: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙是怎樣
Comment: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過是個腦袋不怎麼好的巨人嘛
Comment: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,伊安班長
Comment: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前門有兩個接近
Comment: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,分別是10公尺級跟6公尺級!
Comment: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,後方也有一個
Comment: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,12公尺級的巨人正往這裡接近!!
Comment: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,伊安 該撤退了!
Comment: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那小夥子根本沒辦法堵住那個洞
Comment: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是啊
Comment: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒辦法了 把他留在這裡吧
Comment: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,發現精銳小組施放的紅色信號彈!
Comment: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看來封鎖作戰發生了很嚴重的問題
Comment: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,白白去送死
Comment: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,同伴們...
Comment: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,根本就是白白去送死
Comment: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 快看那個
Comment: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼? 怎麼了!
Comment: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,失敗了嗎...?
Comment: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼...
Comment: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂! 阿爾敏你要去哪?
Comment: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,皮克希斯司令
Comment: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該要立刻恢復成防衛大門的狀態
Comment: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,您意下如何?
Comment: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不需要
Comment: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請下令精銳小組撤退...
Comment: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒必要
Comment: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,繼續讓巨人聚集到角落來
Comment: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,關於精銳小組的話
Comment: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我已經全權交給他們在現場處理了
Comment: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他們不只是本事高強
Comment: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還是背負著人類命運的最精銳
Comment: 0,0:06:57.78,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不容許他們如此輕易就認輸
Comment: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了不讓死去的士兵們白白犧牲
Comment: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,凡是能夠嘗試的事都給我做到底
Comment: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 你在猶豫什麼?
Comment: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點指揮啊!
Comment: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,伊安 這又不是你的錯!
Comment: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這原本就是毫無意義的作戰
Comment: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大家都很清楚!
Comment: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然有嘗試的價值
Comment: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過我們做得夠多了!
Comment: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,聽好了!
Comment: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們班要爬上牆去!
Comment: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,慢著!
Comment: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等一下...
Comment: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,冷靜點 阿卡曼
Comment: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,里柯班
Comment: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,去對付後方12公尺級的!
Comment: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米塔比班和我這一班去對付前面那兩隻!
Comment: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說什麼?
Comment: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,被賦予指揮權的人是我!
Comment: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我閉嘴遵從命令
Comment: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不能丟下毫無防備的葉卡
Comment: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,作戰計畫改變了
Comment: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,直到回收葉卡為止
Comment: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,保護他免於遭受巨人的攻擊
Comment: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他對人類來說是一個珍貴的可能性
Comment: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,並不是可以這麼簡單就捨去的東西
Comment: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為他和我們不同
Comment: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有人能夠取代他
Comment: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了那個失控的人類兵器
Comment: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明光是這次就有數百人死了
Comment: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道將他回收後要再讓同樣的狀況重演嗎?
Comment: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯...
Comment: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不管犧牲多少人 都應該要不斷地挑戰!
Comment: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連他怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏自己一個人往那邊去了
Comment: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我想應該是沒事吧
Comment: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該?
Comment: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一定沒事的
Comment: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連他做得到
Comment: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將巨人聚集到城市的角落
Comment: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我只覺得是浪費時間
Comment: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以巨人為對手的戰鬥一定會變成消耗戰
Comment: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在目前的階段
Comment: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是想避免士兵的陣亡吧?
Comment: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,意思是在現在這個階段死去的士兵是白白送死?
Comment: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,遲早會變成一場大戰的!
Comment: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了那個時候的到來
Comment: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而儲備兵力將犧牲降低至最小限度是理所當然的
Comment: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,上頭是正確的
Comment: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是這樣嗎?
Comment: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是這樣!
Comment: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,既然如此 那就以將犧牲降至最小來行動吧
Comment: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們彼此都是
Comment: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,伊安你瘋了嗎？
Comment: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼妳告訴我人類要怎麼樣才能戰勝巨人啊?
Comment: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,里柯 妳說啊!
Comment: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要怎麼做才能夠突破目前的狀況
Comment: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能保住人類的本性!
Comment: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且還可以不必死!
Comment: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,戰勝巨人那壓倒性的力量!
Comment: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要如何才能辦到?
Comment: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要如何戰勝巨人...
Comment: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我怎麼可能會知道...
Comment: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以我們現在該做的事情
Comment: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只剩下這個了
Comment: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了這個還搞不清楚的人類兵器
Comment: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只能拼了我們的老命去
Comment: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,完成任務!
Comment: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,很悲慘對吧
Comment: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們人類唯一能做的竟然是這種事
Comment: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好了 該怎麼辦?
Comment: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是我們能夠進行的戰鬥
Comment: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是我們被賦予的垂死掙扎
Comment: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那種事情 我無法認同
Comment: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂! 里柯!
Comment: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我會遵從作戰行動的
Comment: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我覺得你所說得沒有錯
Comment: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我會讓他們知道被逼到絕境的人類的恐怖
Comment: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為我無法認同自己是白白去送死
Comment: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,後面的12公尺級就交給我們班吧
Comment: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧! 我們還要應付前面那兩個
Comment: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是啊!
Comment: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,謝謝你 伊安班長
Comment: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿卡曼...
Comment: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,無須道謝
Comment: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不知道妳會做出什麼事 所以捏了把冷汗
Comment: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過妳可以依照當初的作戰自由行動
Comment: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那樣才能發揮妳的實力
Comment: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好的!
Comment: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,畢竟妳是為了保護男朋友嘛
Comment: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是家人...
Comment: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,奇怪?
Comment: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,破損的地方沒有修復
Comment: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是因為之前的傷嗎?
Comment: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對艾連的影響呢?
Comment: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,再說 有辦法保證艾連可以恢復原貌嗎?
Comment: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,算了...
Comment: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這不是我自己隨便想想就能知道的
Comment: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在我只能做我自己做得到的事
Comment: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連...
Comment: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎...
Comment: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,究竟怎麼了...
Comment: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,CM
Comment: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,奇怪
Comment: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我...
Comment: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在... 到底在做什麼...
Comment: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我現在坐著嗎?
Comment: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼都看不見
Comment: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,今天是幾號了?
Comment: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這裡是...
Comment: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼啊
Comment: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是家裡啊...
Comment: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,睡覺吧...
Comment: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在做什麼? 艾連
Comment: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,聽好了 總而言之就是讓巨人不要從那個角落離開
Comment: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要專注於這一點 集中注意力
Comment: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,了解了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們沒有必要與巨人交戰
Comment: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,訓練兵以三人一組在地上跑
Comment: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到了牆壁邊的話就往上面飛 千萬別死啊
Comment: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,萬一有漏掉的巨人就由我們來打倒
Comment: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,萬一?
Comment: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是十分之一的機率嗎?
Comment: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們發現有危險的時候
Comment: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,依照自己的判斷來行動也沒差嗎?
Comment: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果這樣可以成功的話
Comment: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,基爾休坦班出發
Comment: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是!
Comment: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,糟糕... 後面!
Comment: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有一個13公尺級朝著葉卡接近中
Comment: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大門的方向陸續有新的巨人進來了!
Comment: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大約是10公尺級的四個!
Comment: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿卡曼 後面的麻煩妳了!
Comment: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,了解!
Comment: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別讓巨人接近葉卡!
Comment: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這裡就要攔下來!
Comment: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,了解!
Comment: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算是精銳 要兩個班同時對付4個巨人也太....
Comment: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼會...
Comment: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼巨人們都...
Comment: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類的數目又不多
Comment: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道...是被艾連所吸引?
Comment: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,作戰如何了?
Comment: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連他到底怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,很危險 你快離開
Comment: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個巨人並沒有艾連的意志!
Comment: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我對他說話也都沒有反應!
Comment: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不管是誰來做都已經沒有意義了!
Comment: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,作戰呢?
Comment: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,失敗了!
Comment: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為不能丟下艾連
Comment: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以大家都在奮戰!
Comment: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是再這麼下去
Comment: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人太多 可能會導致全軍覆沒!
Comment: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從頭部後方到脖子...
Comment: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,長1公尺!
Comment: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,寬10公分!
Comment: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏?
Comment: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我要試著把艾連拖出來!
Comment: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎妳別讓其他巨人靠近這裡!
Comment: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你要幹嘛...
Comment: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連是從巨人的弱點部位出來的...
Comment: 0,0:15:55.53,0:16:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個和巨人的本質之謎應該有所關連...
Comment: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別擔心...
Comment: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要避開正中央的部位!
Comment: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不會死掉的
Comment: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,頂多就只是...
Comment: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有點痛而已
Comment: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏!
Comment: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏 你別亂來!
Comment: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎!
Comment: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在只需做妳能做的事!
Comment: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要米卡莎過去一定會有人能因此得救!
Comment: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連就交給我 妳快去!
Comment: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連 你聽得見嗎?
Comment: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你要振作啊!
Comment: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果你不出來我們大家都會死的!
Comment: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,千萬別輸給巨人的身體!
Comment: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,反正你快點就對了趕快離開這團肉塊!
Comment: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要我從這裡出來?
Comment: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼?
Comment: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我現在...很睏啊...
Comment: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快出來
Comment: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快一點
Comment: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你媽的仇不報了嗎!!
Comment: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你不是要把巨人殺光嗎?
Comment: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你不是痛恨那些殺死你媽的傢伙嗎!!
Comment: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在說什麼啊阿爾敏?
Comment: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我媽就在這裡啊
Comment: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連! 艾連!
Comment: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快清醒過來啊!
Comment: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在裡面吧?
Comment: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果你繼續待在裡面的話
Comment: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,會被巨人殺死的!
Comment: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那樣的話一切都會在此結束!
Comment: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就說了
Comment: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我根本不知道你在說什麼 阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼非要出去不可...
Comment: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是說啊
Comment: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼一定要出去...
Comment: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,幹嘛加入調查軍團...
Comment: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,即使不願意 也只能憑自己的判斷來行動了
Comment: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,得手了!
Comment: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總算是倒下來了 可惡的傢伙!
Comment: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,暫時保持距離
Comment: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿卡曼回來了!
Comment: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,與米塔比班會合!
Comment: 0,0:18:58.29,0:18:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,奇怪...
Comment: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰!
Comment: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點去!
Comment: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不要再有人因為我而死了
Comment: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡 在這種時候故障
Comment: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰!
Comment: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼不使用立體機動裝置?
Comment: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道!
Comment: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,故障了嗎!?
Comment: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總會有辦法啦!
Comment: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,畜生!
Comment: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我在扯人後腿是怎樣
Comment: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有什麼辦法了嗎...
Comment: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們不是說好總有一天要去外面的世界探險嗎?
Comment: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在牆外很遙遠的地方
Comment: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有著會燃燒的水
Comment: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,冰凍的大地
Comment: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還有一望無際的沙的雪原
Comment: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是我的爸爸與媽媽試圖想去的世界
Comment: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,或許你已經忘記了
Comment: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你之所以不再提起那些
Comment: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不就是因為不想讓我加入調查軍團嗎?
Comment: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,外面的...世界...
Comment: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,回答我
Comment: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一旦走出牆外
Comment: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明就是個地獄般的世界
Comment: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有可能像我爸媽一樣
Comment: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以悽慘的死法死去
Comment: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼艾連還是想去外面的世界呢?
Comment: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你問我為什麼?
Comment: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這還需要你問嗎?
Comment: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為我 就是出生在這世界上的啊!
Comment: 0,0:22:08.71,0:22:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:23:53.73,0:23:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,去吧 跑吧 生存下去吧
Comment: 0,0:23:57.14,0:24:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在許多的話語交錯及眾多生命凋零而去的戰場上
Comment: 0,0:24:02.54,0:24:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連背起希望
Comment: 0,0:24:04.77,0:24:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,朝向城門
